        <title>Shared bicycle</title>
        <published>2023-08-25T14:09:14.183+00:00</published>
        <updated>2023-08-25T14:09:14.183+00:00</updated>
        <author>
          <name>Unknown</name>
        </author>
        <link rel="alternate" href="https://longfangsong.github.io/first-week-in-chalmers/docs/transport/shared-bicycle/" type="text/html"/>
        <id>https://longfangsong.github.io/first-week-in-chalmers/docs/transport/shared-bicycle/</id>
        
        <content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Note: In Sweden, wearing a helmet when riding a bicycle is only mandatory up to the age of 15. However, it is always the safest choice to wear a helmet even if it’s not mandatory.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You can rent a shared bicycle by using &lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;styrochstall.se&#x2F;sv&#x2F;&quot;&gt;Styr &amp;amp; Ställ&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;longfangsong.github.io&#x2F;first-week-in-chalmers&#x2F;docs&#x2F;transport&#x2F;shared-bicycle&#x2F;IMG_140FF85DD9D6-1.jpeg&quot; alt=&quot;Alt text&quot; &#x2F;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Register needs a Sweden phone number.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;After registration, you can use the app to rent a bicycle.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;student-discount&quot;&gt;Student discount&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you have registered on mecenant, you can get a student discount for a year&#x27;s rent.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Just search for &amp;quot;Styr &amp;amp; Ställ&amp;quot; on mecenant. You will find the discount code.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;longfangsong.github.io&#x2F;first-week-in-chalmers&#x2F;docs&#x2F;transport&#x2F;shared-bicycle&#x2F;IMG_A3FA63F59171-1.jpeg&quot; alt=&quot;Alt text&quot; &#x2F;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Copy the code and paste it into the app.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;longfangsong.github.io&#x2F;first-week-in-chalmers&#x2F;docs&#x2F;transport&#x2F;shared-bicycle&#x2F;IMG_5A3BEEF66F01-1.jpeg&quot; alt=&quot;Alt text&quot; &#x2F;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;longfangsong.github.io&#x2F;first-week-in-chalmers&#x2F;docs&#x2F;transport&#x2F;shared-bicycle&#x2F;IMG_74606B0B506B-1.jpeg&quot; alt=&quot;Alt text&quot; &#x2F;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Then you can rent a bicycle for a year, with 225kr paid.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
</content>
        
